code: public static ChainedCxfEndpointConfigurer create(CxfEndpointConfigurer parent, CxfEndpointConfigurer child) {     ChainedCxfEndpointConfigurer result = new ChainedCxfEndpointConfigurer().     result.parent = parent.     result.child = child.     return result. }

public ChainedCxfEndpointConfigurer addChild(CxfEndpointConfigurer cxfEndpointConfigurer) {     ChainedCxfEndpointConfigurer result = new ChainedCxfEndpointConfigurer().     result.parent = this.     result.child = cxfEndpointConfigurer.     return result. }
@Override public void configureClient(Client client) {     parent.configureClient(client).     child.configureClient(client). }
@Override public void configureServer(Server server) {     parent.configureServer(server).     child.configureServer(server). }
